    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>, CDCDistSQLStatementVisitor<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CDCDistSQLStatementVisitor
    public class CDCDistSQLStatementBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements CDCDistSQLStatementVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of CDCDistSQLStatementVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
